      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Success和Error都要能回到Idle。Success那边是Reset，Error这边是Retry。但Error还有一个特殊出口——如果重试也没用，要触发Security_IntrusionDetection做入侵检测。",
